<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 p-3 md:p-6 transition-colors duration-300"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <div class="space-y-6">

    <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">Segna con una X le risposte corrette.</p>

    <!-- Container ESERCIZI -->
    <div class="p-4 md:p-6 bg-orange-100 dark:bg-orange-900/30 rounded-2xl space-y-8">

      <!-- Esercizio 1 -->
      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
          <%= numero_esercizio_badge(1) %>
          Tre amici osservano l'immagine accanto e fanno le seguenti affermazioni. Chi non dice una cosa vera?
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
          <div class="shrink-0">
            <%= image_tag "nvi4_mat/p143/p143_01.jpg", class: "max-w-full h-auto dark:bg-white dark:rounded-lg dark:p-2" %>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 space-y-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <p>Mauro dice: "I segmenti AC e BD sono le diagonali del quadrilatero".</p>
            <p>Alice dice: "I segmenti AC e BD sono perpendicolari".</p>
            <p>Mattia dice: "I segmenti AC e BD sono assi di simmetria".</p>
            <div class="space-y-2 mt-4">
              <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded">
                <input type="radio" name="q1" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
                <span>Mauro.</span>
              </label>
              <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded">
                <input type="radio" name="q1" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
                <span>Alice.</span>
              </label>
              <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded">
                <input type="radio" name="q1" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="true">
                <span>Mattia.</span>
              </label>
              <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded">
                <input type="radio" name="q1" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
                <span>Tutti e tre.</span>
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Esercizio 2 -->
      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
          <%= numero_esercizio_badge(2) %>
          In quale poligono non è stata tracciata correttamente l'altezza?
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
          <%= image_tag "nvi4_mat/p143/p143_02.jpg", class: "max-w-full h-auto dark:bg-white dark:rounded-lg dark:p-2" %>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-2">
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q2" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
            <span>A</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q2" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="true">
            <span>B</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q2" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
            <span>C</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q2" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
            <span>D</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Esercizio 3 -->
      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
          <%= numero_esercizio_badge(3) %>
          Quanti centimetri misura il perimetro della figura?
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
          <%= image_tag "nvi4_mat/p143/p143_03.jpg", class: "max-w-full h-auto dark:bg-white dark:rounded-lg dark:p-2" %>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-2">
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q3" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
            <span>8 cm</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q3" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
            <span>12 cm</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q3" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="true">
            <span>16 cm</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q3" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
            <span>20 cm</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Esercizio 4 -->
      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
          <%= numero_esercizio_badge(4) %>
          Osserva la figura: a quale frazione dell'area del triangolo ABC corrisponde quella del quadrato arancione?
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-6">
          <%= image_tag "nvi4_mat/p143/p143_04.jpg", class: "max-w-full h-auto dark:bg-white dark:rounded-lg dark:p-2" %>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="1/4" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Esercizio 5 -->
      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
          <%= numero_esercizio_badge(5) %>
          A quanti chilometri quadrati corrispondono 1324 hm²?
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-2">
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q5" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="true">
            <span>13,24 km²</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q5" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
            <span>1,324 km²</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q5" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
            <span>0,1324 km²</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q5" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
            <span>132,4 km²</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Esercizio 6 -->
      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
          <%= numero_esercizio_badge(6) %>
          Se il lato di un quadrato misura 9 cm, quanto misura la sua area?
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-2">
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q6" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
            <span>18 cm²</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q6" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="true">
            <span>81 cm²</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q6" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
            <span>90 cm²</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q6" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
            <span>100 cm²</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Esercizio 7 -->
      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
          <%= numero_esercizio_badge(7) %>
          Serena disegna sul quaderno un triangolo isoscele con la base lunga 8 cm e l'altezza di 12 cm. Qual è il calcolo corretto per trovare l'area del triangolo?
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-2">
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q7" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
            <span>8 × 12</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q7" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="true">
            <span>(8 × 12) : 2</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q7" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
            <span>(8 + 12) : 2</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q7" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
            <span>8 + 12 + 2</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Esercizio 8 -->
      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
          <%= numero_esercizio_badge(8) %>
          Quanto misura l'area di questo trapezio isoscele?
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
          <%= image_tag "nvi4_mat/p143/p143_05.jpg", class: "max-w-full h-auto dark:bg-white dark:rounded-lg dark:p-2" %>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-2">
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q8" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
            <span>102 mm²</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q8" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="true">
            <span>290 mm²</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q8" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
            <span>580 mm²</span>
          </label>
          <label class="flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 p-2 rounded border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <input type="radio" name="q8" class="w-5 h-5" data-correct-answer="false">
            <span>1 160 mm²</span>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
  </div>
</div>
